                <h5 class="card-title" id="itineraryTitle">Day 2</h5>
                <h6>MORNING</h6>
                <p class="card-text">Start your morning with a hearty breakfast at Brunch Cafe. Their menu has an array of options that are certain to please your whole family. Take a quick walk to the St. Charles History Museum to shop for local items and learn all about the history of the city.
                  ​</p>
                  <h6>AFTERNOON</h6>
                <p class="card-text">After a good meal, head to Hickory Knolls - 130 acres of woodlands, wetlands, prairies and a discovery center full of FREE nature activities, including animals that reside there. </p>
                  <h6>EVENING</h6>
                <p class="card-text">Enjoy a relaxing evening and catch the newest movie at Charlestowne 18 or enjoy a night of bowling at St. Charles Bowl. End the night with a delicious treat from Frozen Yogurt.
                 ​</p>
